Load Layer
→ Layer → Add Layer → Add Vector Layer → Select IND_rails.

Open Attribute Table
→ Right-click IND_rails → Open Attribute Table.

Enable Editing
→ Click Toggle Editing (pencil icon).

Open Field Calculator
→ Click Field Calculator (calculator icon).

Create New Field

Name: Track_Len
Type: Decimal Number
Expression: $length / 1000
Save Edits
→ Click Toggle Editing → Save changes.

Run Statistics
→ Vector → Analysis Tools → Basic Statistics for Fields.

Input Layer: IND_rails
Field: Track_Len
→ Click Run.
